            <h1  class="xs:text-3xl font-bold md:text-8xl md:text-white">
              Maternal Record Pro
            </h1>

            <p class="mt-3 mb-5 md:text-lg xs:text-md md:text-white">
              <span class="font-italic"
                >A project under Digital Solutions for Maternal Health (DS4MH),
                an initiative of Theodora Anavhe Adamu Foundation (TAAF)
              </span>
              <br />
              <br />
              MaternalRecordPro is a digital platform that automates manual
              record-keeping systems in primary healthcare centers across
              Nigeria. <br> By replacing outdated paper records with a seamless
              digital process, we empower:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-outside mx-5 list-disc md:text-white">
              <li>Pregnant women to receive better care.</li>
              <li>
                Midwives & record officers to manage health data efficiently.
              </li>
              <li>
                M&E staff & policymakers to track maternal health outcomes.
              </li>
            </ul>
